    dc:creator "Loughman, Zachary J.; Thoma, Roger F.; Fetzner Jr, James W.; Stocker, G. Whitney" ;
    dc:date "2015" ;
    dc:title "Cambarus (Jugicambarus) pauleyi, a new species of crayfish (Decapoda: Cambaridae) endemic to southcentral West Virginia, USA, with a re-description of Cambarus (J.) dubius" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239953>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239949>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239952>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239954>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239955> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239953>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Illustration of various morphological features of Cambarus pauleyi, new species. (A.) lateral view of carapace; (B.) dorsal view of carapace; (C.) epistome; (D.) antennal scale; (E.) dorsal view of distal podomere of right cheliped of form I male; (F.) ischial hook of form I male; (G.) lateral (left) and mesial (right) view of left first gonopod of form I male; (H.) annulus ventralis; (I.) lateral (left) and mesial (right) view of form II male gonopod. A – G from holotype; H from allotype; I from morphotype." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/239953/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239949>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Illustration of various morphological features of Cambarus dubius sensu stricto, as herein defined. (A.) lateral view of carapace; (B.) dorsal view of carapace; (C.) epistome; (D.) antennal scale; (E.) dorsal view of distal podomere of right cheliped of form I male; (F.) ischial hook of form I male; (G.) lateral (left) and mesial (right) view of left first gonopod of form I male; (H.) annulus ventralis; (I.) lateral (left) and mesial (right) view of form II male gonopod. A – G from holotype; H from WLU 2050 b (female); I from WLU 2050 a (form II male)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/239949/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239952>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Known range of Cambarus dubius sensu stricto in Maryland, Pennsylvania and West Virginia." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/239952/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239954>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. A specimen of Cambarus pauleyi from the type location showing typical life colors." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/239954/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.239955>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Known range of Cambarus pauleyi, new species in West Virginia." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/239955/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

